[Guest]: Now, we should have put a caveat in the starting that one of the reasons that the fact that,

02:19:55.300 --> 02:20:00.900
[Guest]: you know, whatever decisions you take, right, there is so much, like, risk-taking, right?

02:20:00.900 --> 02:20:02.900
[Guest]: I mean, if you talk about probability, right?

02:20:02.900 --> 02:20:06.180
[Guest]: You know, sometimes when, you know, my friends from college, they say, you know,

02:20:10.980 --> 02:20:13.860
[Guest]: You know, I was like, I'm happy for you.

02:20:13.860 --> 02:20:19.540
[Guest]: But boss, if you think objectively about what is risk, you have to think about the worst-case

02:20:19.540 --> 02:20:20.740
[Guest]: scenario, right?

