03:40:14.840 --> 03:40:15.800
[Guest]: where I've exactly written

03:40:15.800 --> 03:40:16.840
[Guest]: what I felt.

03:40:16.840 --> 03:40:17.880
[Guest]: Why I left.

03:40:17.880 --> 03:40:18.440
[Guest]: And, you know,

03:40:18.440 --> 03:40:19.240
[Guest]: anytime I'm like,

03:40:19.240 --> 03:40:20.440
[Guest]: my boss was so generous

03:40:21.000 --> 03:40:22.120
[Guest]: at the time that,

03:40:22.120 --> 03:40:23.480
[Guest]: I don't know if there are

03:40:23.480 --> 03:40:24.680
[Guest]: 25-year-old reporters

03:40:25.240 --> 03:40:25.800
[Guest]: who get like,

03:40:25.800 --> 03:40:26.760
[Guest]: my boss gave me freedom,

03:40:26.760 --> 03:40:27.320
[Guest]: that boss,

03:40:27.960 --> 03:40:29.000
[Guest]: don't forget daily.

03:40:29.000 --> 03:40:29.800
[Guest]: You take one month

03:40:29.800 --> 03:40:30.600
[Guest]: to write one story,

03:40:30.600 --> 03:40:32.200
[Guest]: I'll give you one page in the paper.

03:40:32.200 --> 03:40:32.520
[Guest]: Right?

03:40:32.520 --> 03:40:33.480
[Guest]: That was the promise he made

03:40:33.480 --> 03:40:34.440
[Guest]: and he used to do that.

03:40:35.080 --> 03:40:36.280
[Guest]: So, I used to think,

03:40:36.280 --> 03:40:37.080
[Guest]: have I gone mad?

03:40:37.080 --> 03:40:38.040
[Guest]: Like, who...

03:40:38.040 --> 03:40:40.040
[Guest]: The HT real estate.

03:40:40.040 --> 03:40:40.760
[Guest]: In your head, you know,

03:40:40.760 --> 03:40:41.240
[Guest]: it's like,

03:40:41.240 --> 03:40:42.440
[Guest]: so many million copies go,

03:40:42.440 --> 03:40:43.640
[Guest]: you know, people read.

03:40:43.640 --> 03:40:44.760
[Guest]: So, I sometimes felt that,

03:40:44.760 --> 03:40:45.880
[Guest]: I wasn't a fool.

03:40:45.880 --> 03:40:47.080
[Guest]: Like, you left that opportunity.

03:40:47.080 --> 03:40:48.280
[Guest]: But I had that page in my diary.

03:40:49.080 --> 03:40:49.480
[Guest]: You know,

03:40:49.480 --> 03:40:49.960
[Guest]: which is why

03:40:49.960 --> 03:40:51.240
[Guest]: that thing about moral compass,

03:40:51.240 --> 03:40:52.040
[Guest]: I think that

03:40:52.040 --> 03:40:53.560
[Guest]: my journal holds me accountable.

03:40:54.200 --> 03:40:55.400
[Guest]: Can you talk more about that

03:40:55.400 --> 03:40:56.920
[Amit Varma]: or you're not comfortable?

03:40:56.920 --> 03:40:58.200
[Guest]: About that incident.

03:40:58.200 --> 03:40:59.720
[Guest]: Okay, I won't go

03:40:59.720 --> 03:41:00.680
[Guest]: into specific concrete.

03:41:00.680 --> 03:41:01.320
[Guest]: There's another story

03:41:01.320 --> 03:41:01.960
[Guest]: I can tell you

03:41:01.960 --> 03:41:02.760
[Guest]: in another institution.

03:41:02.760 --> 03:41:03.320
[Guest]: But in this,

03:41:03.320 --> 03:41:04.280
[Guest]: there's a story I wrote,

03:41:05.160 --> 03:41:06.840
[Guest]: which had something to do

03:41:06.840 --> 03:41:07.560
[Guest]: with the prime minister.

03:41:07.560 --> 03:41:08.280
[Guest]: But it was not,

03:41:09.080 --> 03:41:09.640
[Guest]: honestly, I mean,

03:41:09.640 --> 03:41:10.520
[Guest]: it's not a story that,

03:41:11.160 --> 03:41:11.720
[Guest]: I'll say that,

03:41:11.720 --> 03:41:12.360
[Guest]: I, you know,

03:41:12.360 --> 03:41:13.480
[Guest]: like, I broke this story.

03:41:13.480 --> 03:41:14.680
[Guest]: It was, I broke this story.

03:41:14.680 --> 03:41:17.320
[Guest]: I thought it's a normal story.

03:41:17.320 --> 03:41:18.440
[Guest]: My editor just sat on it.

03:41:19.160 --> 03:41:19.400
[Guest]: Okay.

03:41:20.120 --> 03:41:21.560
[Guest]: My problem was not sometimes,

03:41:21.560 --> 03:41:22.280
[Guest]: you know, see,

03:41:22.280 --> 03:41:23.480
[Guest]: I'm not an idiot that

03:41:23.480 --> 03:41:24.760
[Guest]: I don't know the pressures

03:41:24.760 --> 03:41:26.040
[Guest]: that editors face,

03:41:26.040 --> 03:41:26.440
[Guest]: you know.

03:41:26.440 --> 03:41:27.880
[Guest]: And I think one of the

03:41:27.880 --> 03:41:28.840
[Guest]: most inspiring things

03:41:28.840 --> 03:41:29.560
[Guest]: inside newsrooms

03:41:29.560 --> 03:41:31.080
[Guest]: is to see editors,

03:41:31.880 --> 03:41:33.160
[Guest]: who despite knowing

03:41:33.160 --> 03:41:34.200
[Guest]: all the pressures,

03:41:34.200 --> 03:41:35.000
[Guest]: fight their way out

03:41:35.000 --> 03:41:35.960
[Guest]: to get a story in the paper.

03:41:35.960 --> 03:41:37.080
[Guest]: I hope that

03:41:37.080 --> 03:41:38.120
[Guest]: if readers could see,

03:41:38.920 --> 03:41:40.520
[Guest]: you know, the daily fights

03:41:40.520 --> 03:41:42.040
[Guest]: that journalists

03:41:43.000 --> 03:41:44.440
[Guest]: fight inside the newsroom

03:41:44.440 --> 03:41:46.280
[Guest]: to get things in the paper,

03:41:46.280 --> 03:41:47.960
[Guest]: despite the pressures,

03:41:49.000 --> 03:41:50.200
[Guest]: you know, the model of,

03:41:50.200 --> 03:41:50.680
[Guest]: you know, this,

03:41:50.680 --> 03:41:51.640
[Guest]: so I don't like this phrasing

03:41:51.640 --> 03:41:52.760
[Guest]: of Godi media,

03:41:52.760 --> 03:41:54.120
[Guest]: you know, I like Ravish,

03:41:54.120 --> 03:41:55.640
[Guest]: but this whole Godi media

03:41:55.640 --> 03:41:56.680
[Guest]: framing makes me,

03:41:56.680 --> 03:41:58.280
[Guest]: it's a very simplistic narrative.

03:41:58.280 --> 03:41:59.560
[Guest]: Because individuals fight

03:41:59.560 --> 03:42:00.840
[Guest]: within these places.

03:42:00.840 --> 03:42:01.880
[Guest]: Yeah, and see,

03:42:01.880 --> 03:42:03.000
[Guest]: if something gets published,

03:42:03.000 --> 03:42:04.200
[Guest]: then you won't know

03:42:04.200 --> 03:42:05.160
[Guest]: what's behind it.

03:42:05.160 --> 03:42:07.320
[Guest]: If something is not published,

03:42:07.320 --> 03:42:08.520
[Guest]: then you'll know,

03:42:08.520 --> 03:42:09.400
[Guest]: like I'm telling you now,

03:42:09.400 --> 03:42:10.280
[Guest]: then you'll feel,

03:42:10.280 --> 03:42:10.600
[Guest]: you know,

03:42:11.160 --> 03:42:11.880
[Guest]: there is a problem.

03:42:11.880 --> 03:42:12.360
[Guest]: So I'm saying,

03:42:13.000 --> 03:42:13.800
[Guest]: when things are normal,

03:42:13.800 --> 03:42:14.600
[Guest]: you don't know that

03:42:15.560 --> 03:42:16.280
[Guest]: there's something more

03:42:16.280 --> 03:42:16.920
[Guest]: that has happened

03:42:17.480 --> 03:42:18.760
[Guest]: to see what you're reading

03:42:18.760 --> 03:42:19.640
[Guest]: that way, you know?

03:42:20.440 --> 03:42:21.560
[Guest]: So, and that goes up

03:42:21.560 --> 03:42:23.080
[Guest]: to the level of proprietors,

03:42:23.080 --> 03:42:23.560
[Guest]: because, you know,

03:42:23.560 --> 03:42:25.080
[Guest]: now I try to talk

03:42:25.080 --> 03:42:25.960
[Guest]: to a lot of senior people

03:42:25.960 --> 03:42:26.760
[Guest]: in my profession

03:42:26.760 --> 03:42:29.240
[Guest]: rather than people in 20s,

03:42:29.240 --> 03:42:30.760
[Guest]: because I want to know from them,

03:42:30.760 --> 03:42:32.600
[Guest]: you know, what has changed?

03:42:32.600 --> 03:42:33.480
[Guest]: What are you seeing?

03:42:33.480 --> 03:42:34.760
[Guest]: And I'm fortunate that

03:42:35.400 --> 03:42:36.200
[Guest]: a lot of senior people

03:42:36.200 --> 03:42:36.760
[Guest]: in this profession

03:42:36.760 --> 03:42:37.640
[Guest]: have given me time

03:42:37.640 --> 03:42:38.680
[Guest]: one-to-one,

03:42:38.680 --> 03:42:39.480
[Guest]: telling me like

03:42:40.280 --> 03:42:41.240
[Guest]: detailed stories

03:42:41.240 --> 03:42:42.440
[Guest]: about their interactions

03:42:42.440 --> 03:42:43.800
[Guest]: with proprietors,

03:42:43.800 --> 03:42:44.600
[Guest]: you know,

03:42:44.600 --> 03:42:45.720
[Guest]: challenges they have faced.

03:42:45.720 --> 03:42:47.080
[Guest]: And that really inspires me

03:42:47.080 --> 03:42:47.720
[Guest]: that they have stuck

03:42:47.720 --> 03:42:48.520
[Guest]: to this profession.

03:42:49.240 --> 03:42:49.720
[Guest]: They know,

03:42:50.440 --> 03:42:51.640
[Guest]: and they are in the top positions,

03:42:51.640 --> 03:42:52.200
[Guest]: you know, so anyway.

03:42:52.760 --> 03:42:54.040
[Guest]: So the point I was trying

03:42:54.040 --> 03:42:54.920
[Guest]: to make that in HD,

03:42:55.640 --> 03:42:56.600
[Guest]: this is my editor

03:42:56.600 --> 03:42:57.720
[Guest]: sat on a story.

03:42:57.720 --> 03:42:58.600
[Guest]: My problem was not

03:43:00.200 --> 03:43:00.920
[Guest]: you sat on a story.

03:43:00.920 --> 03:43:01.640
[Guest]: The problem was

03:43:02.920 --> 03:43:03.800
[Guest]: you ignored it.

03:43:05.000 --> 03:43:06.120
[Guest]: You come and tell me,

03:43:06.120 --> 03:43:08.280
[Guest]: boss, there's a problem.

03:43:08.280 --> 03:43:09.560
[Guest]: You just behaved as if

03:43:09.560 --> 03:43:10.680
[Guest]: nothing happened,

03:43:10.680 --> 03:43:11.180
[Guest]: you know,

03:43:13.480 --> 03:43:14.840
[Guest]: that there's no story.

03:43:14.840 --> 03:43:16.040
[Guest]: You just pretend as if,

03:43:16.600 --> 03:43:17.160
[Guest]: and that,

03:43:19.000 --> 03:43:19.800
[Guest]: you know, it's just,

03:43:21.400 --> 03:43:22.840
[Guest]: I don't know, like, how can I,

03:43:24.040 --> 03:43:26.280
[Guest]: like, how will I find the motivation

03:43:26.280 --> 03:43:27.320
[Guest]: to work on my next story?

03:43:27.880 --> 03:43:28.840
[Guest]: I used to write

03:43:28.840 --> 03:43:29.960
[Amit Varma]: for a major newspaper.

03:43:29.960 --> 03:43:31.080
[Amit Varma]: And I won't take names,

03:43:31.080 --> 03:43:32.600
[Amit Varma]: but I mean, it's guessable.

03:43:32.600 --> 03:43:34.360
[Unknown]: And my thing with them was that

03:43:34.360 --> 03:43:35.480
[Amit Varma]: even if they change a word

03:43:35.480 --> 03:43:36.200
[Amit Varma]: in my column,

03:43:36.200 --> 03:43:37.400
[Amit Varma]: they have to send a playback

03:43:37.400 --> 03:43:38.120
[Amit Varma]: and I'll approve it.

03:43:38.120 --> 03:43:39.560
[Amit Varma]: And all that, and they knew

03:43:39.560 --> 03:43:40.840
[Amit Varma]: I was very particular about that.

03:43:41.800 --> 03:43:43.080
[Amit Varma]: So one day my editor

03:43:43.080 --> 03:43:44.280
[Amit Varma]: kind of called me

03:43:44.280 --> 03:43:45.560
[Amit Varma]: just when the playback was due

03:43:45.560 --> 03:43:46.680
[Amit Varma]: and she was almost in tears.

03:43:47.480 --> 03:43:48.760
[Amit Varma]: And she said, Amit,

03:43:48.760 --> 03:43:49.960
[Amit Varma]: I wanted to call you

03:43:49.960 --> 03:43:50.600
[Amit Varma]: and speak to you

03:43:50.600 --> 03:43:51.880
[Amit Varma]: because if I just send you a mail,

03:43:51.880 --> 03:43:53.320
[Amit Varma]: I know you'll get very angry.

03:43:53.320 --> 03:43:54.440
[Amit Varma]: That in your column,

03:43:54.440 --> 03:43:55.160
[Amit Varma]: and it was, of course,

03:43:55.160 --> 03:43:56.840
[Amit Varma]: very critical of the government.

03:43:56.840 --> 03:43:58.200
[Amit Varma]: And even in the past,

03:43:58.200 --> 03:43:59.240
[Amit Varma]: this newspaper had carried

03:43:59.240 --> 03:44:00.280
[Amit Varma]: many columns by me,

03:44:00.280 --> 03:44:01.400
[Amit Varma]: very critical of the government,

03:44:01.400 --> 03:44:02.280
[Amit Varma]: including when I had

03:44:02.280 --> 03:44:03.960
[Amit Varma]: blasted demonetization,

03:44:03.960 --> 03:44:05.160
[Amit Varma]: a piece that was, you know,

03:44:05.160 --> 03:44:06.520
[Unknown]: retweeted by Rahul Gandhi

03:44:06.520 --> 03:44:07.080
[Unknown]: and Kejriwal.

03:44:07.080 --> 03:44:08.520
[Unknown]: And everyone.

03:44:09.400 --> 03:44:10.360
[Amit Varma]: And she said that

03:44:10.360 --> 03:44:11.720
[Amit Varma]: I know you'll get angry,

03:44:11.720 --> 03:44:13.400
[Amit Varma]: but there is one sentence

03:44:13.400 --> 03:44:14.040
[Amit Varma]: I have to cut

03:44:14.680 --> 03:44:16.040
[Amit Varma]: and I am sort of,

03:44:16.040 --> 03:44:17.160
[Amit Varma]: I have to cut it.

03:44:17.160 --> 03:44:18.600
[Amit Varma]: And it's because we have been,

03:44:18.600 --> 03:44:19.800
[Amit Varma]: there's been a lot of pressure

03:44:19.800 --> 03:44:22.040
[Amit Varma]: from above and about

03:44:22.040 --> 03:44:23.720
[Amit Varma]: two people in particular,

03:44:23.720 --> 03:44:25.000
[Amit Varma]: you know, me and somebody else.

03:44:25.000 --> 03:44:25.480
[Amit Varma]: I won't name,

03:44:25.480 --> 03:44:26.600
[Amit Varma]: but a person who's been

03:44:26.600 --> 03:44:27.400
[Amit Varma]: a guest on my show.

03:44:27.400 --> 03:44:28.840
[Unknown]: And all this is easy to guess.

03:44:28.840 --> 03:44:29.720
[Unknown]: Yeah, very easy.

03:44:29.720 --> 03:44:31.320
[Amit Varma]: And there have been complaints

03:44:31.320 --> 03:44:32.360
[Amit Varma]: about the two of you

03:44:32.360 --> 03:44:33.960
[Amit Varma]: and there's a lot of pressure.

03:44:33.960 --> 03:44:36.040
[Unknown]: So I'll just cut this one sentence

03:44:36.040 --> 03:44:37.640
[Unknown]: and I let the rest of it stay.

03:44:39.000 --> 03:44:40.120
[Amit Varma]: And what do you want to do?

03:44:41.880 --> 03:44:43.560
[Amit Varma]: And the rest of the column

03:44:43.560 --> 03:44:44.520
[Amit Varma]: was very critical.

03:44:44.520 --> 03:44:45.800
[Amit Varma]: So I said, keep it.

03:44:45.800 --> 03:44:47.160
[Amit Varma]: You know, if it's just at one line,

03:44:47.720 --> 03:44:48.520
[Amit Varma]: it's fine.

03:44:48.520 --> 03:44:49.160
[Amit Varma]: The rest of it,

03:44:49.160 --> 03:44:50.520
[Amit Varma]: it's basically saying

03:44:50.520 --> 03:44:51.720
[Unknown]: what I want to say.

03:44:51.720 --> 03:44:52.920
[Amit Varma]: And if you kind of go to

03:44:52.920 --> 03:44:53.880
[Amit Varma]: indiancut.com

03:44:53.880 --> 03:44:55.000
[Amit Varma]: and you go to the original piece,

03:44:55.000 --> 03:44:56.280
[Unknown]: you can make out what the line is,

03:44:56.280 --> 03:44:56.760
[Unknown]: but whatever,

03:44:56.760 --> 03:44:57.560
[Amit Varma]: it doesn't really matter.

03:44:58.200 --> 03:44:59.640
[Amit Varma]: And then I started thinking about,

03:44:59.640 --> 03:45:01.480
[Amit Varma]: okay, what is the correct

03:45:01.480 --> 03:45:02.760
[Unknown]: course of action for me now?

03:45:03.560 --> 03:45:05.240
[Amit Varma]: And this other person

03:45:05.240 --> 03:45:06.120
[Amit Varma]: in the same boat as me

03:45:06.120 --> 03:45:07.480
[Amit Varma]: chose not to write for them anymore.

03:45:08.280 --> 03:45:09.240
[Amit Varma]: And my question was,

03:45:09.240 --> 03:45:10.360
[Amit Varma]: okay, what do I do

03:45:10.360 --> 03:45:12.120
[Amit Varma]: if I give up this space?

03:45:12.120 --> 03:45:13.400
[Amit Varma]: And it's an important space

03:45:13.400 --> 03:45:14.840
[Amit Varma]: in a big newspaper,

03:45:14.840 --> 03:45:17.080
[Amit Varma]: then the space might be taken

03:45:17.080 --> 03:45:18.200
[Amit Varma]: by somebody who is more

03:45:18.200 --> 03:45:19.160
[Amit Varma]: client to the government.

03:45:19.800 --> 03:45:20.360
[Amit Varma]: Right.

03:45:20.360 --> 03:45:21.720
[Amit Varma]: So should I continue to fight

03:45:21.720 --> 03:45:22.520
[Amit Varma]: in small ways

03:45:22.520 --> 03:45:23.800
[Amit Varma]: in whatever way I can,

03:45:23.800 --> 03:45:25.240
[Amit Varma]: or should I give it up?

03:45:25.240 --> 03:45:26.600
[Amit Varma]: So I made a choice to keep writing.

03:45:26.600 --> 03:45:27.320
[Amit Varma]: I think I wrote one

03:45:27.320 --> 03:45:28.200
[Amit Varma]: or two more pieces for them.

03:45:28.200 --> 03:45:29.560
[Amit Varma]: And then I gave it up anyway,

03:45:29.560 --> 03:45:31.080
[Amit Varma]: because of the sort of logic

03:45:31.080 --> 03:45:31.880
[Amit Varma]: I went into earlier.

03:45:33.880 --> 03:45:34.840
[Unknown]: There's no point writing

03:45:34.840 --> 03:45:35.720
[Amit Varma]: for anybody else.

03:45:37.240 --> 03:45:38.600
[Amit Varma]: But, and I want to underscore

03:45:38.600 --> 03:45:40.840
[Amit Varma]: that point that these are,

03:45:40.840 --> 03:45:41.880
[Amit Varma]: you know, editors

03:45:41.880 --> 03:45:43.560
[Amit Varma]: in all of these places

03:45:43.560 --> 03:45:44.840
[Amit Varma]: at an individual level,

03:45:45.640 --> 03:45:46.600
[Amit Varma]: have had to face

03:45:46.600 --> 03:45:47.640
[Amit Varma]: very difficult choices.

03:45:47.640 --> 03:45:48.280
[Amit Varma]: Absolutely.

03:45:48.280 --> 03:45:49.160
[Amit Varma]: And they have fought

03:45:49.160 --> 03:45:49.720
[Amit Varma]: the good fight.

03:45:49.720 --> 03:45:50.280
[Unknown]: Yeah.

03:45:50.280 --> 03:45:50.680
[Unknown]: You know?

03:45:50.680 --> 03:45:51.080
[Unknown]: Yeah.

03:45:51.080 --> 03:45:52.120
[Unknown]: These people carried

03:45:52.840 --> 03:45:54.200
[Amit Varma]: countless critical pieces

03:45:54.200 --> 03:45:56.200
[Amit Varma]: by me of this particular government

03:45:56.200 --> 03:45:57.640
[Amit Varma]: in the harshest possible terms.

03:45:58.360 --> 03:45:59.560
[Amit Varma]: But it's just the incentives

03:45:59.560 --> 03:46:00.120
[Amit Varma]: of the game.

03:46:00.120 --> 03:46:01.160
[Amit Varma]: It's not that the people

03:46:01.160 --> 03:46:01.720
[Guest]: are craven,

03:46:01.720 --> 03:46:02.600
[Guest]: that they are bad,

03:46:02.600 --> 03:46:03.160
[Guest]: nothing.

03:46:03.160 --> 03:46:04.200
[Guest]: It's just the incentives.

03:46:04.200 --> 03:46:04.600
[Guest]: Exactly.

03:46:04.600 --> 03:46:06.200
[Guest]: And I think that is what makes,

03:46:06.200 --> 03:46:06.840
[Guest]: you know, which is why

03:46:06.840 --> 03:46:08.200
[Guest]: I keep saying to my friends,

03:46:08.200 --> 03:46:09.880
[Guest]: like, I'd really love to talk

03:46:09.880 --> 03:46:11.160
[Guest]: to people outside the press

03:46:11.160 --> 03:46:12.600
[Guest]: about how the media works.

03:46:12.600 --> 03:46:13.240
[Guest]: Like, you know, I have

03:46:13.800 --> 03:46:15.080
[Guest]: what I saw in the seven years.

03:46:15.800 --> 03:46:17.160
[Guest]: And this is a point

03:46:17.160 --> 03:46:19.240
[Guest]: that we should not be complacent.

03:46:19.240 --> 03:46:20.040
[Guest]: We, you know,

03:46:20.040 --> 03:46:21.080
[Guest]: my model is that

03:46:22.600 --> 03:46:23.400
