[Amit Varma]: it's a man bites dog all the time.

04:10:38.120 --> 04:10:39.720
[Amit Varma]: But that's not it.

04:10:39.720 --> 04:10:42.440
[Amit Varma]: There's more than supply and demand

04:10:42.440 --> 04:10:43.480
[Amit Varma]: and even supply and demand

04:10:43.480 --> 04:10:44.760
[Amit Varma]: is so often guesswork

04:10:44.760 --> 04:10:46.920
[Amit Varma]: and thinking along predictable lines.

04:10:46.920 --> 04:10:48.520
[Amit Varma]: So give me a sense

04:10:48.520 --> 04:10:50.040
[Amit Varma]: of this fundamental basic

04:10:50.040 --> 04:10:50.600
[Amit Varma]: and I understand

04:10:50.600 --> 04:10:52.280
[Amit Varma]: it's a very large question,

04:10:52.280 --> 04:10:54.280
[Amit Varma]: but what should a newsroom cover?

04:10:54.840 --> 04:10:56.760
[Amit Varma]: You know, and at one level,

04:10:56.760 --> 04:10:58.040
[Amit Varma]: that big meta question

04:10:58.040 --> 04:10:59.640
[Amit Varma]: and at the other level,

04:10:59.640 --> 04:11:01.240
[Amit Varma]: give me a sense of the state

04:11:01.240 --> 04:11:03.560
[Amit Varma]: of the modern newsroom in India,

04:11:03.560 --> 04:11:05.640
[Amit Varma]: because the whole system

04:11:05.640 --> 04:11:07.240
[Amit Varma]: just seems to be broken,

04:11:07.240 --> 04:11:08.360
[Amit Varma]: you know, in India today,

04:11:08.360 --> 04:11:09.560
[Amit Varma]: of course, you've described

04:11:09.560 --> 04:11:11.640
[Amit Varma]: a particular set of incentives

04:11:11.640 --> 04:11:12.520
[Amit Varma]: in a particular kind

04:11:12.520 --> 04:11:13.960
[Amit Varma]: of political context.

04:11:13.960 --> 04:11:15.800
[Amit Varma]: But give me a sense of, you know,

04:11:15.800 --> 04:11:17.560
[Amit Varma]: these two diametrically

04:11:17.560 --> 04:11:18.520
[Amit Varma]: different things, you know,

04:11:18.520 --> 04:11:19.880
[Amit Varma]: sort of how do you ask

04:11:19.880 --> 04:11:21.000
[Amit Varma]: that philosophical question

04:11:21.000 --> 04:11:21.960
[Amit Varma]: to begin with?

04:11:21.960 --> 04:11:23.480
[Amit Varma]: And what are things like now?

04:11:25.480 --> 04:11:27.960
[Guest]: So let me just try to see

04:11:27.960 --> 04:11:28.600
[Guest]: how to articulate.

04:11:28.600 --> 04:11:30.840
[Guest]: So I think let's just describe

04:11:30.840 --> 04:11:31.800
[Guest]: the problem more clearly.

04:11:32.440 --> 04:11:34.600
[Guest]: So this is sense of newsworthiness.

04:11:35.240 --> 04:11:36.280
[Guest]: This is newsworthy.

04:11:36.280 --> 04:11:38.040
[Guest]: I don't think any editor

04:11:38.040 --> 04:11:40.200
[Guest]: in this country, new media, old media,

04:11:41.000 --> 04:11:43.240
[Guest]: can they write a one page

04:11:43.240 --> 04:11:44.280
[Guest]: 10 point description?

04:11:45.000 --> 04:11:47.080
[Guest]: This is our mental model.

04:11:47.880 --> 04:11:49.240
[Guest]: What is newsworthy?

04:11:49.240 --> 04:11:50.680
[Guest]: I don't think anyone can write it.

04:11:50.680 --> 04:11:53.240
[Guest]: Do you think that there are criteria?

04:11:53.240 --> 04:11:54.120
[Guest]: What makes news?

04:11:54.120 --> 04:11:54.840
[Guest]: What doesn't make news?

04:11:54.840 --> 04:11:56.040
[Guest]: I don't think so.

04:11:56.040 --> 04:11:56.840
[Amit Varma]: It's arbitrary.

04:11:56.840 --> 04:11:58.040
[Amit Varma]: At best, you can come up

04:11:58.040 --> 04:11:59.320
[Amit Varma]: with subjective criteria.

04:11:59.320 --> 04:12:01.720
[Amit Varma]: That for me as an editor,

04:12:01.720 --> 04:12:03.080
[Amit Varma]: this is what I feel

04:12:03.080 --> 04:12:04.680
[Amit Varma]: our publication should cover.

04:12:04.680 --> 04:12:06.760
[Guest]: But it's subjective and it's limited.

04:12:06.760 --> 04:12:08.120
[Guest]: And also like a very subjective,

04:12:08.120 --> 04:12:09.960
[Guest]: also like you can talk about,

04:12:09.960 --> 04:12:10.440
[Guest]: like you say,

04:12:10.440 --> 04:12:11.800
[Guest]: we want to cover education,

04:12:11.800 --> 04:12:12.840
[Guest]: but the education we're like,

04:12:13.480 --> 04:12:15.160
[Guest]: that's not, that's a topic.

04:12:15.880 --> 04:12:17.560
[Guest]: I'm talking at the story level.

04:12:17.560 --> 04:12:19.000
[Guest]: You know, this news,

04:12:19.000 --> 04:12:20.520
[Guest]: what is newsworthy

04:12:20.520 --> 04:12:22.200
[Guest]: is a very arbitrary construct.

04:12:23.400 --> 04:12:23.960
[Guest]: Right.

04:12:23.960 --> 04:12:25.720
[Guest]: And I think the whole point,

04:12:25.720 --> 04:12:27.640
[Guest]: when the idea of the mainstream existed,

04:12:27.640 --> 04:12:29.000
[Guest]: and you have talked about in the show

04:12:29.640 --> 04:12:32.440
[Guest]: that there's no mainstream

04:12:32.440 --> 04:12:34.120
[Guest]: as such, if you think about it.

04:12:34.680 --> 04:12:36.120
[Guest]: I mean, they have the power

04:12:36.120 --> 04:12:37.080
[Guest]: of amplification,

04:12:37.080 --> 04:12:38.280
[Guest]: but in the larger scheme of things,

04:12:38.280 --> 04:12:40.360
[Guest]: right, like the literal meaning

04:12:40.360 --> 04:12:41.640
[Guest]: of the word, you know.

04:12:42.200 --> 04:12:44.360
[Guest]: So I'm saying that is the issue,

04:12:44.360 --> 04:12:45.960
[Guest]: that newsworthiness,

04:12:45.960 --> 04:12:47.400
[Guest]: I think is just a fundamentally

04:12:47.400 --> 04:12:48.520
[Guest]: arbitrary construct.

04:12:49.560 --> 04:12:50.920
[Guest]: And it's on the whims

04:12:50.920 --> 04:12:52.280
[Guest]: and fancies of editors.

04:12:52.280 --> 04:12:54.040
[Guest]: And what you expect in an ideal world

04:12:54.040 --> 04:12:55.160
[Guest]: is you expect that

04:12:56.040 --> 04:12:57.160
[Guest]: you respect the judgment

04:12:57.160 --> 04:12:57.960
[Guest]: of the editor,

04:12:58.440 --> 04:12:59.080
[Guest]: that, you know,

04:12:59.080 --> 04:13:00.520
[Guest]: that the reason this person

04:13:00.520 --> 04:13:02.520
[Guest]: is leading a publication

04:13:03.080 --> 04:13:04.600
[Guest]: is because they have some sense

04:13:04.600 --> 04:13:05.640
[Guest]: of what is important,

04:13:05.640 --> 04:13:06.840
[Guest]: what is not important,

04:13:06.840 --> 04:13:09.160
[Guest]: and that drives what is being covered.

04:13:09.160 --> 04:13:10.040
[Guest]: Now, the challenge here is,

04:13:10.040 --> 04:13:12.280
[Guest]: I think there's a framework

04:13:12.280 --> 04:13:14.200
[Guest]: called the theory of interlocking public.

04:13:14.200 --> 04:13:15.400
[Guest]: Have you heard of this term?

04:13:15.400 --> 04:13:15.880
[Unknown]: No.

04:13:15.880 --> 04:13:18.360
[Guest]: So the big picture of this frame

04:13:18.360 --> 04:13:19.560
[Guest]: is that, see,

04:13:20.360 --> 04:13:23.000
[Guest]: you talk about any particular issues,

04:13:25.160 --> 04:13:26.600
[Guest]: and you talk about citizens.

04:13:26.600 --> 04:13:27.800
[Guest]: Everyone is not going to be

04:13:27.800 --> 04:13:28.760
[Guest]: interested in every issue.

04:13:28.760 --> 04:13:30.360
[Guest]: Some people are interested in something

04:13:30.360 --> 04:13:31.640
[Guest]: and they are completely ignorant

04:13:31.640 --> 04:13:32.520
[Guest]: about something else.

04:13:33.160 --> 04:13:34.840
[Guest]: And then the thing will change

04:13:35.400 --> 04:13:36.200
[Guest]: in another context.

04:13:37.000 --> 04:13:37.560
[Guest]: Right?

04:13:37.560 --> 04:13:39.160
[Guest]: So the way I think about

04:13:39.160 --> 04:13:40.600
[Guest]: a lot of mainstream publications

04:13:40.600 --> 04:13:42.680
[Guest]: is that they cater to the narrow elite

04:13:43.240 --> 04:13:45.960
[Guest]: about what is interesting,

04:13:45.960 --> 04:13:46.760
[Guest]: what is relevant.

04:13:47.480 --> 04:13:50.680
[Guest]: So when you talk about political news,

04:13:51.480 --> 04:13:52.760
[Guest]: you know, one of the things that, again,

04:13:52.760 --> 04:13:54.280
[Guest]: I never understood the logic,

04:13:54.280 --> 04:13:56.360
[Guest]: you know, reporters take so much pride

04:13:56.360 --> 04:13:57.320
[Guest]: in quote-unquote,

04:13:57.320 --> 04:13:59.560
[Guest]: in quote-unquote, breaking a story

04:14:00.440 --> 04:14:01.640
[Guest]: that the government is anyway

04:14:01.640 --> 04:14:03.000
[Guest]: going to tell you two days later.

04:14:03.000 --> 04:14:03.880
[Guest]: And you say,

04:14:03.880 --> 04:14:05.240
[Guest]: there's nothing that they're hiding.

04:14:05.240 --> 04:14:07.080
[Guest]: It's just that you read this first in X.

04:14:07.880 --> 04:14:09.320
[Guest]: So I never understood that.

04:14:11.320 --> 04:14:11.880
[Guest]: So what?

04:14:12.600 --> 04:14:14.360
[Guest]: Agar aapne mujhe do din pehle bata diya.

04:14:15.480 --> 04:14:15.980
[Guest]: Right?

04:14:17.080 --> 04:14:18.440
[Guest]: Like insignificant thing.

04:14:19.000 --> 04:14:21.160
[Guest]: It's not enhancing my understanding.

04:14:21.160 --> 04:14:22.920
[Guest]: But that is what the newsroom incentivizes.

04:14:22.920 --> 04:14:23.880
[Guest]: You know, when they say,

04:14:23.880 --> 04:14:25.320
[Guest]: we want exclusive,

04:14:25.320 --> 04:14:26.200
[Guest]: we want scoops.

04:14:26.200 --> 04:14:28.200
[Guest]: So what I like is that information

04:14:28.200 --> 04:14:29.720
[Guest]: that will anyway come out

04:14:29.720 --> 04:14:30.760
[Guest]: in the public sphere, na?

04:14:30.760 --> 04:14:32.360
[Guest]: Everyone will get it, but you...

04:14:32.360 --> 04:14:33.800
[Guest]: So I'm saying this,

04:14:33.800 --> 04:14:35.400
[Guest]: but this is a metric of newsworthiness

04:14:35.400 --> 04:14:37.480
[Guest]: that we have it first, incentives.

04:14:38.840 --> 04:14:40.680
[Guest]: So this journalism professor,

04:14:40.680 --> 04:14:41.960
[Guest]: I think, Jay Rosen in the US,

04:14:41.960 --> 04:14:43.480
[Guest]: he gave this very good statement.

04:14:43.480 --> 04:14:44.040
[Guest]: He said,

04:14:44.040 --> 04:14:45.400
[Guest]: the modern media ecosystem

04:14:46.120 --> 04:14:47.800
[Guest]: is not designed

04:14:48.600 --> 04:14:50.600
[Guest]: to enhance public understanding.

04:14:50.600 --> 04:14:53.400
[Guest]: It is enhanced to manufacture new content.

04:14:53.400 --> 04:14:55.400
[Guest]: And he included the big public media

04:14:55.400 --> 04:14:56.600
[Guest]: in the big publications.

04:14:57.320 --> 04:14:58.120
[Guest]: So that way,

04:14:58.120 --> 04:14:59.400
[Guest]: that's a description of the problem

04:14:59.400 --> 04:15:01.720
[Guest]: that I would want as a reader,

04:15:01.720 --> 04:15:02.680
[Guest]: that I just,

04:15:02.680 --> 04:15:04.040
[Guest]: I want to understand India better.

04:15:04.040 --> 04:15:05.640
[Guest]: I want to understand this government better.

04:15:06.600 --> 04:15:08.040
[Guest]: But you get into...

04:15:08.040 --> 04:15:09.480
[Guest]: And you can't even say that

04:15:09.480 --> 04:15:11.080
[Guest]: the stories that are being reported

04:15:11.080 --> 04:15:12.280
[Guest]: are irrelevant.

04:15:12.280 --> 04:15:13.800
[Guest]: But I think that what has happened

04:15:13.800 --> 04:15:15.880
[Guest]: is that at least now that I'm outside

04:15:15.880 --> 04:15:16.920
[Guest]: and I read,

04:15:16.920 --> 04:15:18.040
[Guest]: you feel so alienated.

04:15:18.760 --> 04:15:19.640
[Guest]: That you know, okay, like,

04:15:20.280 --> 04:15:21.560
[Guest]: toh like aap main kya karoon?

04:15:21.560 --> 04:15:22.060
[Unknown]: You know?

04:15:22.060 --> 04:15:24.940
[Guest]: And the conflicting part here is that,

04:15:24.940 --> 04:15:25.580
[Guest]: you know,

04:15:25.580 --> 04:15:27.180
[Guest]: sometimes there's a friend of mine,

04:15:27.180 --> 04:15:27.900
[Guest]: very good journalist,

04:15:27.900 --> 04:15:28.460
[Guest]: he said,

04:15:28.460 --> 04:15:29.580
[Guest]: sometimes we write the story

04:15:29.580 --> 04:15:30.700
[Guest]: because we just want

04:15:30.700 --> 04:15:31.900
[Guest]: that person in the RBI

04:15:32.620 --> 04:15:33.420
[Guest]: to know that, you know,

04:15:33.420 --> 04:15:34.060
[Guest]: we have written this

04:15:34.060 --> 04:15:35.340
[Guest]: so that a change happens.

04:15:35.980 --> 04:15:36.940
[Guest]: You know, they have this in the head

04:15:36.940 --> 04:15:38.220
[Guest]: that this story is written

04:15:38.220 --> 04:15:39.420
[Guest]: for certain people.

04:15:39.980 --> 04:15:40.480
[Guest]: Right?

04:15:42.540 --> 04:15:43.040
[Unknown]: So,

04:15:45.100 --> 04:15:46.140
[Guest]: the answer that

04:15:46.140 --> 04:15:47.500
[Guest]: what a newspaper ought to do,

04:15:49.740 --> 04:15:51.340
[Guest]: I have never been able to do

04:15:51.340 --> 04:15:52.140
[Guest]: I have never been able to

04:15:52.140 --> 04:15:53.340
[Guest]: crack this answer that,

04:15:54.300 --> 04:15:55.340
[Guest]: ki like if I am,

04:15:55.340 --> 04:15:57.180
[Guest]: I'm asked to write guidelines,

04:15:57.180 --> 04:15:58.300
[Guest]: kaise likhenge?

04:15:58.300 --> 04:15:59.500
[Guest]: Like, remember the conference

04:15:59.500 --> 04:16:01.100
[Guest]: we were talking about the CRISPR?

04:16:01.100 --> 04:16:01.660
[Unknown]: Yeah.

04:16:01.660 --> 04:16:02.140
[Guest]: Right?

04:16:02.140 --> 04:16:03.100
[Guest]: So CRISPR,

04:16:03.100 --> 04:16:03.980
[Guest]: like just for context

04:16:03.980 --> 04:16:05.260
[Guest]: for those who don't know,

04:16:05.260 --> 04:16:07.340
[Guest]: revolutionary technology in gene editing.

04:16:07.340 --> 04:16:07.840
[Guest]: Right?

04:16:08.620 --> 04:16:09.580
[Guest]: People should read about it

04:16:09.580 --> 04:16:10.300
[Guest]: and understand that

04:16:10.300 --> 04:16:11.900
[Guest]: something big is happening

04:16:11.900 --> 04:16:12.780
[Guest]: that can change

04:16:12.780 --> 04:16:14.860
[Guest]: how human evolution happens.

04:16:14.860 --> 04:16:15.360
[Guest]: Right?

04:16:16.140 --> 04:16:16.860
[Guest]: It's not like it's,

04:16:17.820 --> 04:16:19.100
[Guest]: like tax policy changes,

04:16:19.100 --> 04:16:19.740
[Guest]: you know,

04:16:19.740 --> 04:16:21.100
[Guest]: once in a while, you know?

04:16:21.100 --> 04:16:22.060
[Guest]: This you're talking about

04:16:22.860 --> 04:16:23.660
[Amit Varma]: something big.

04:16:23.660 --> 04:16:24.780
[Amit Varma]: I had an episode on it

04:16:24.780 --> 04:16:25.660
[Amit Varma]: with Shambhavi Naik,

04:16:25.660 --> 04:16:27.340
[Guest]: I'll link that from the show notes.

04:16:27.340 --> 04:16:27.840
[Guest]: But,

04:16:28.780 --> 04:16:29.740
[Guest]: on a day-to-day basis,

04:16:29.740 --> 04:16:30.240
[Guest]: we,

04:16:30.860 --> 04:16:32.380
[Guest]: most people would be unaware, right?

04:16:32.380 --> 04:16:32.940
[Guest]: So I'm saying

04:16:32.940 --> 04:16:34.300
[Guest]: if there is a theory of importance,

04:16:35.340 --> 04:16:36.060
[Guest]: what matters,

04:16:36.060 --> 04:16:37.180
[Guest]: what does not matter?

04:16:37.180 --> 04:16:37.680
[Guest]: Right?

04:16:38.940 --> 04:16:39.820
[Guest]: Does this not matter?

04:16:40.460 --> 04:16:41.340
[Guest]: So I'm saying this is a way

04:16:41.340 --> 04:16:42.300
[Guest]: that I pose a question.

04:16:42.940 --> 04:16:43.820
[Guest]: Right? That okay,

04:16:43.820 --> 04:16:44.540
[Guest]: what is happening?

04:16:45.420 --> 04:16:46.940
[Guest]: And in the theory of interlocking public,

04:16:46.940 --> 04:16:47.980
[Guest]: that was the point that

04:16:48.540 --> 04:16:49.580
[Guest]: how do you even come up

04:16:49.580 --> 04:16:50.540
[Guest]: with a list of topics

04:16:50.540 --> 04:16:51.740
[Guest]: that cater to the masses?

04:16:51.740 --> 04:16:52.460
[Guest]: Because,

04:16:52.460 --> 04:16:53.660
[Guest]: there is no one public.

04:16:53.660 --> 04:16:55.180
[Guest]: The public is so disaggregated.

04:16:55.180 --> 04:16:56.300
[Guest]: They have so much

04:16:56.300 --> 04:16:57.500
[Guest]: disaggregated interests.

04:16:58.300 --> 04:16:58.800
[Guest]: So,

04:16:59.500 --> 04:17:00.940
[Guest]: I don't know the answer to the question

04:17:00.940 --> 04:17:02.460
[Guest]: that what a newsroom should cover.

04:17:03.180 --> 04:17:04.620
[Guest]: I think of it as a different way

04:17:04.620 --> 04:17:05.340
[Guest]: that you,

04:17:05.340 --> 04:17:06.860
[Guest]: when I say first principles,

04:17:06.860 --> 04:17:07.820
[Guest]: it's more about that

04:17:07.820 --> 04:17:08.700
[Guest]: when you have a story,

04:17:09.340 --> 04:17:09.900
[Guest]: you know?

04:17:09.900 --> 04:17:11.340
[Guest]: At least that's how I think about my work.

04:17:11.340 --> 04:17:12.380
[Guest]: You think about, okay,

04:17:12.380 --> 04:17:13.100
[Guest]: why does it matter?

04:17:13.740 --> 04:17:14.380
[Guest]: Story, you know,

04:17:14.380 --> 04:17:15.420
[Guest]: how does it matter?

04:17:15.420 --> 04:17:16.620
[Guest]: And you report it vigorously

04:17:16.620 --> 04:17:17.820
[Guest]: and make it relevant.

04:17:17.820 --> 04:17:19.100
[Guest]: It's not that every story you read

04:17:19.100 --> 04:17:20.540
[Guest]: has to have some actionable.

04:17:20.540 --> 04:17:21.100
[Guest]: Like,

04:17:21.100 --> 04:17:22.300
[Guest]: do you know what was his name?

04:17:22.300 --> 04:17:23.020
[Guest]: Aaron Schwartz.

04:17:24.300 --> 04:17:24.800
[Guest]: You know, the,

04:17:25.580 --> 04:17:26.080
[Guest]: you know,

04:17:26.620 --> 04:17:27.580
[Guest]: the internet's own boy.

04:17:27.580 --> 04:17:28.620
[Guest]: That's a great documentary,

04:17:28.620 --> 04:17:29.120
[Guest]: which,

04:17:29.660 --> 04:17:30.460
[Guest]: like, really moved me.

04:17:30.460 --> 04:17:32.460
[Guest]: But he was this young hacker

04:17:32.460 --> 04:17:32.940
[Guest]: in the US,

04:17:32.940 --> 04:17:33.820
[Guest]: very politically active,

04:17:33.820 --> 04:17:34.380
[Guest]: but also,

04:17:34.380 --> 04:17:35.580
[Guest]: I think he co-founded Reddit.

04:17:36.460 --> 04:17:37.020
[Guest]: Reddit, yes,

04:17:37.020 --> 04:17:37.500
[Guest]: I think he did.

04:17:37.500 --> 04:17:38.060
[Guest]: Yeah.

04:17:38.060 --> 04:17:39.100
[Guest]: So, he committed suicide

04:17:39.100 --> 04:17:39.740
[Guest]: because of this whole

04:17:40.380 --> 04:17:42.220
[Guest]: JSTOR thing about academic papers.

04:17:42.220 --> 04:17:43.180
[Guest]: So, he had a great blog.

04:17:43.180 --> 04:17:43.900
[Guest]: It's still online.

04:17:43.900 --> 04:17:45.100
[Guest]: And he wrote a piece

04:17:45.100 --> 04:17:46.860
[Guest]: about why he doesn't read the news.

04:17:46.860 --> 04:17:48.460
[Amit Varma]: Yeah, he's a guy who got prosecuted,

04:17:48.460 --> 04:17:49.500
[Amit Varma]: I think, for putting up

04:17:49.500 --> 04:17:51.260
[Guest]: JSTOR papers online for free.

04:17:51.260 --> 04:17:51.580
[Guest]: Yeah.

04:17:51.580 --> 04:17:52.380
[Guest]: Very sad, very sad.

04:17:52.380 --> 04:17:52.940
[Guest]: Very sad, right?

04:17:52.940 --> 04:17:54.060
[Guest]: So, I was reading his blog

04:17:54.060 --> 04:17:54.620
[Guest]: and I thought,

04:17:54.620 --> 04:17:55.260
[Guest]: ki boss,

04:17:55.260 --> 04:17:55.900
[Guest]: this guy,

04:17:55.900 --> 04:17:57.020
[Guest]: if you look at his politics,

04:17:57.980 --> 04:17:58.460
[Guest]: like,

04:17:58.460 --> 04:17:59.260
[Guest]: day in, day out,

04:17:59.260 --> 04:18:01.020
[Guest]: this guy is making political change.

04:18:01.020 --> 04:18:02.220
[Guest]: He's thinking about politics.

04:18:02.220 --> 04:18:03.820
[Guest]: And he has a post on his website,

04:18:03.820 --> 04:18:05.100
[Guest]: I don't read the news

04:18:05.100 --> 04:18:06.460
[Guest]: because news is irrelevant

04:18:06.460 --> 04:18:07.020
[Guest]: to what I do.

04:18:07.820 --> 04:18:08.220
[Guest]: He says,

04:18:08.220 --> 04:18:09.340
[Guest]: I open the page

04:18:09.340 --> 04:18:09.740
[Guest]: and I say,

04:18:09.740 --> 04:18:10.300
[Guest]: this is happening,

04:18:10.300 --> 04:18:11.260
[Guest]: that is happening.

04:18:11.260 --> 04:18:11.820
[Guest]: But he says,

04:18:11.820 --> 04:18:14.140
[Guest]: I don't know where I fit in.

04:18:14.140 --> 04:18:15.340
[Guest]: You know, I can't relate.

04:18:15.900 --> 04:18:16.380
[Guest]: He says, okay,

04:18:16.380 --> 04:18:17.100
[Guest]: you know, something bad

04:18:17.100 --> 04:18:18.060
[Guest]: is happening at that place.

04:18:18.060 --> 04:18:19.340
[Guest]: So, like,

04:18:19.340 --> 04:18:20.300
[Guest]: so he felt that

04:18:20.300 --> 04:18:21.500
[Guest]: I don't feel the agency

04:18:22.060 --> 04:18:23.420
[Guest]: that these bad things are happening,

04:18:23.420 --> 04:18:24.540
[Guest]: but what can I do?

04:18:24.540 --> 04:18:26.220
[Guest]: So, I'm saying that is one frame of reference

04:18:26.220 --> 04:18:27.100
[Guest]: where someone can say,

04:18:28.140 --> 04:18:28.860
[Guest]: so what I'm,

04:18:28.860 --> 04:18:29.660
[Guest]: so I can,

04:18:29.660 --> 04:18:30.460
[Guest]: it's going in,

04:18:30.460 --> 04:18:31.100
[Guest]: I'm meandering,

04:18:31.100 --> 04:18:32.540
[Guest]: but the point I'm trying to make is that

04:18:34.380 --> 04:18:36.460
[Guest]: everything that largely we are seeing,

04:18:36.460 --> 04:18:37.980
[Guest]: you can poke holes on why

04:18:40.220 --> 04:18:41.660
[Guest]: the way we currently think

04:18:41.660 --> 04:18:42.620
[Guest]: has big issues.

04:18:43.260 --> 04:18:44.060
[Guest]: Okay, it's broken.

04:18:44.940 --> 04:18:46.140
[Guest]: And there is no solution

04:18:46.140 --> 04:18:46.860
[Guest]: that you can say,

04:18:46.860 --> 04:18:47.180
[Guest]: you know,

04:18:47.180 --> 04:18:49.100
[Guest]: if Samarth Mansal is tomorrow,

04:18:49.100 --> 04:18:49.900
[Guest]: the editor of a paper,

04:18:50.780 --> 04:18:51.660
[Guest]: right?

04:18:51.660 --> 04:18:52.540
[Guest]: I am not saying that

04:18:52.540 --> 04:18:53.980
[Guest]: I have an answer that

04:18:53.980 --> 04:18:54.860
[Guest]: I am going to fix it.

04:18:55.820 --> 04:18:56.300
[Guest]: Right?

04:18:56.300 --> 04:18:57.100
[Guest]: Because the,

04:18:58.060 --> 04:18:58.620
[Guest]: because this,

04:18:58.620 --> 04:19:00.140
[Guest]: the fundamental assumption is that

04:19:00.940 --> 04:19:02.540
[Guest]: something deserves to be news

04:19:03.180 --> 04:19:04.300
[Guest]: and something does not

04:19:04.300 --> 04:19:05.260
[Guest]: deserve to be news.

04:19:05.260 --> 04:19:06.940
[Guest]: I don't think that distinction is relevant,

04:19:07.900 --> 04:19:09.260
[Guest]: but on a day-to-day basis,

04:19:09.260 --> 04:19:10.380
[Guest]: whatever you are covering,

04:19:10.380 --> 04:19:11.420
[Guest]: right, and how you report

04:19:12.060 --> 04:19:13.580
[Guest]: and how you tell a story,

04:19:13.580 --> 04:19:15.420
[Guest]: I think that is where I feel

04:19:15.420 --> 04:19:17.260
[Guest]: that you can list down rules,

04:19:17.260 --> 04:19:18.700
[Guest]: that at least whatever you are doing

04:19:19.340 --> 04:19:20.220
[Guest]: and what are the things

04:19:20.220 --> 04:19:21.100
[Guest]: that have no meaning,

04:19:21.100 --> 04:19:22.300
[Guest]: you can remove that,

04:19:22.300 --> 04:19:23.260
[Guest]: where you say,

04:19:23.260 --> 04:19:24.140
[Guest]: and just experiment

04:19:24.140 --> 04:19:24.460
[Guest]: and you know,

04:19:24.460 --> 04:19:25.900
[Guest]: tell better stories.

04:19:25.900 --> 04:19:26.700
[Guest]: I don't know if that

04:19:26.700 --> 04:19:27.900
[Guest]: answers your question,

04:19:27.900 --> 04:19:28.540
[Guest]: but I'm saying,

04:19:29.260 --> 04:19:29.660
[Guest]: for me,

04:19:29.660 --> 04:19:30.300
[Guest]: what matters is

04:19:30.300 --> 04:19:31.180
[Guest]: what stories I choose.

04:19:32.140 --> 04:19:33.420
[Amit Varma]: Yeah, I don't think this show

04:19:33.420 --> 04:19:34.780
[Amit Varma]: is really about answering questions,

04:19:34.780 --> 04:19:35.740
[Amit Varma]: but more just

04:19:36.860 --> 04:19:37.740
[Amit Varma]: finding questions,

04:19:37.740 --> 04:19:39.180
[Amit Varma]: finding better questions to ask

04:19:39.180 --> 04:19:40.140
[Amit Varma]: and kind of understanding

04:19:40.140 --> 04:19:41.820
[Unknown]: those questions a little better.

04:19:41.820 --> 04:19:42.380
[Unknown]: And you know,

04:19:42.380 --> 04:19:43.260
[Unknown]: for something like this,

04:19:43.260 --> 04:19:44.060
[Amit Varma]: I think that

04:19:44.060 --> 04:19:45.260
[Amit Varma]: there's no definitive answer

04:19:45.260 --> 04:19:46.380
[Amit Varma]: to what you should cover.

04:19:46.380 --> 04:19:47.420
[Amit Varma]: And the ideal way

04:19:47.420 --> 04:19:49.020
[Amit Varma]: is let a thousand flowers bloom.

04:19:49.020 --> 04:19:49.500
[Amit Varma]: Absolutely.

04:19:49.500 --> 04:19:50.300
[Amit Varma]: Let, you know,

04:19:50.300 --> 04:19:51.500
[Amit Varma]: multitudes of people

04:19:51.500 --> 04:19:52.060
[Amit Varma]: get in there,

04:19:52.060 --> 04:19:53.580
[Amit Varma]: do their own kind of reporting,

04:19:53.580 --> 04:19:54.300
[Amit Varma]: and each thing

04:19:54.300 --> 04:19:55.580
[Amit Varma]: will find its own audience.

04:19:55.580 --> 04:19:57.180
[Amit Varma]: And that's what you kind of want.

04:19:57.180 --> 04:19:58.540
[Amit Varma]: But you are right

04:19:58.540 --> 04:19:59.980
[Amit Varma]: that there's a need

04:19:59.980 --> 04:20:01.660
[Amit Varma]: to think about processes

04:20:01.660 --> 04:20:03.020
[Amit Varma]: and to avoid certain traps.

04:20:03.020 --> 04:20:04.700
[Amit Varma]: Like one trap

04:20:04.700 --> 04:20:06.540
[Amit Varma]: that you pointed out

04:20:06.540 --> 04:20:07.500
[Amit Varma]: was, you know,

04:20:07.500 --> 04:20:09.020
[Amit Varma]: the distinction between

04:20:09.020 --> 04:20:10.620
[Amit Varma]: events and systems.

04:20:10.620 --> 04:20:11.500
[Amit Varma]: And you pointed out

04:20:11.500 --> 04:20:13.660
[Amit Varma]: that a lot of news reporting,

04:20:13.660 --> 04:20:15.340
[Amit Varma]: if not pretty much all of it,

04:20:15.340 --> 04:20:17.180
[Amit Varma]: is focused around events.

04:20:17.180 --> 04:20:20.540
[Amit Varma]: Kuch hua, yeh hua, usse report karo.

04:20:20.540 --> 04:20:21.500
[Amit Varma]: And it's,

04:20:21.500 --> 04:20:22.780
[Amit Varma]: and all of it is like that.

04:20:22.780 --> 04:20:24.300
[Amit Varma]: And they don't really contribute

04:20:24.300 --> 04:20:25.580
[Amit Varma]: to public understanding

04:20:25.580 --> 04:20:26.780
[Amit Varma]: to use Jay Rosen's words,

04:20:26.780 --> 04:20:27.820
[Unknown]: like you said.

04:20:27.820 --> 04:20:28.380
[Amit Varma]: You know,

04:20:28.380 --> 04:20:30.940
[Amit Varma]: so just elaborate a little bit

04:20:30.940 --> 04:20:31.740
[Amit Varma]: on, you know,

04:20:32.380 --> 04:20:33.660
[Amit Varma]: thinking in systems

04:20:33.660 --> 04:20:34.620
[Amit Varma]: and thinking in

04:20:34.620 --> 04:20:35.820
[Guest]: just in terms of events.

04:20:35.820 --> 04:20:36.300
[Guest]: Sure.

04:20:36.300 --> 04:20:37.580
[Guest]: So again, I think

04:20:37.580 --> 04:20:38.780
[Guest]: rather than talking in abstract,

04:20:38.780 --> 04:20:39.580
[Guest]: let's be concrete.

04:20:39.580 --> 04:20:39.820
[Guest]: Yeah.

04:20:39.820 --> 04:20:40.540
[Guest]: Okay.

04:20:40.540 --> 04:20:41.340
[Guest]: In 2018,

04:20:41.340 --> 04:20:42.380
[Guest]: there was a story

04:20:42.380 --> 04:20:43.980
[Guest]: which made a lot of headlines,

04:20:43.980 --> 04:20:44.700
[Guest]: which was that

04:20:45.260 --> 04:20:46.700
[Guest]: this current government

04:20:46.700 --> 04:20:48.540
[Guest]: has got powers for surveillance,

04:20:48.540 --> 04:20:49.500
[Guest]: which are significant.

04:20:49.500 --> 04:20:50.220
[Guest]: You know, now

04:20:50.220 --> 04:20:51.020
[Guest]: data from your phone

04:20:51.020 --> 04:20:51.980
[Guest]: will be with the government,

04:20:51.980 --> 04:20:53.180
[Guest]: all of those kinds of things,

04:20:53.180 --> 04:20:54.620
[Guest]: because there was one circular

04:20:54.620 --> 04:20:56.300
[Guest]: that came out in the Home Ministry.

04:20:56.300 --> 04:20:57.820
[Guest]: The Hindu carried something small

04:20:57.820 --> 04:20:59.020
[Guest]: in the inside page.

04:20:59.020 --> 04:20:59.660
[Guest]: But next day,

04:20:59.660 --> 04:21:00.780
[Guest]: that blew on the internet.

04:21:01.420 --> 04:21:02.060
[Guest]: Oh my God,

04:21:02.940 --> 04:21:04.220
[Guest]: what is this government doing?

04:21:04.220 --> 04:21:06.620
[Guest]: Modi is coming after your phones,

04:21:06.620 --> 04:21:07.120
[Guest]: right?

04:21:07.980 --> 04:21:08.540
[Guest]: Again, I don't know

04:21:08.540 --> 04:21:09.260
[Guest]: what happened with the Hindu,

04:21:09.260 --> 04:21:09.980
[Guest]: but it was probably

04:21:09.980 --> 04:21:11.180
[Guest]: some notification came

04:21:11.180 --> 04:21:13.740
[Guest]: and some reporter wrote a copy

04:21:13.740 --> 04:21:15.260
[Guest]: without deep context

04:21:15.260 --> 04:21:16.460
[Guest]: and people misinterpreted

04:21:16.460 --> 04:21:17.340
[Guest]: what had happened.

04:21:17.340 --> 04:21:17.840
[Guest]: Okay.

04:21:18.540 --> 04:21:19.900
[Guest]: TV pe halla ho raha hai,

04:21:19.900 --> 04:21:20.700
[Guest]: Twitter pe halla ho raha hai,

04:21:20.700 --> 04:21:22.060
[Guest]: all of these things are happening.

04:21:22.060 --> 04:21:22.560
[Guest]: Right.

04:21:23.180 --> 04:21:23.980
[Guest]: Then,

04:21:23.980 --> 04:21:24.780
[Guest]: because I was covering

04:21:24.780 --> 04:21:25.980
[Guest]: tech policy at the time,

04:21:26.860 --> 04:21:28.140
[Guest]: like I made phone calls.

04:21:28.140 --> 04:21:29.020
[Guest]: Okay, what is this?

04:21:29.580 --> 04:21:30.380
[Guest]: So this is an event

04:21:30.940 --> 04:21:32.140
[Guest]: which triggered

04:21:32.140 --> 04:21:33.660
[Guest]: a conversation around

04:21:33.660 --> 04:21:34.700
[Guest]: privacy and surveillance,

04:21:34.700 --> 04:21:35.900
[Guest]: which is an important topic.

04:21:35.900 --> 04:21:36.400
[Guest]: Right.

04:21:37.020 --> 04:21:38.700
[Guest]: But the problem was

04:21:38.700 --> 04:21:40.540
[Guest]: everyone was talking about,

04:21:40.540 --> 04:21:41.740
[Guest]: and this is my understanding,

04:21:42.700 --> 04:21:45.020
[Guest]: about a non-existing issue

04:21:45.020 --> 04:21:45.900
[Guest]: because, Amit,

04:21:45.900 --> 04:21:46.940
[Guest]: nothing had changed.

04:21:47.980 --> 04:21:48.480
[Guest]: Okay.

04:21:49.500 --> 04:21:51.020
[Guest]: What, there was no new power.

04:21:52.140 --> 04:21:52.780
[Guest]: The power,

04:21:52.780 --> 04:21:53.340
[Guest]: jo bhi tha,

04:21:53.340 --> 04:21:54.620
[Guest]: it was the existing system.

04:21:54.620 --> 04:21:55.580
[Guest]: It was just that circular,

04:21:55.580 --> 04:21:56.700
[Guest]: which was some formality.

04:21:56.700 --> 04:21:57.260
[Guest]: How I knew?

04:21:57.260 --> 04:21:58.380
[Guest]: Because I made phone calls.

04:21:58.380 --> 04:21:59.420
[Guest]: I called experts

04:21:59.420 --> 04:22:00.140
[Guest]: who covered that.

04:22:00.140 --> 04:22:01.020
[Guest]: I said, look,

04:22:01.020 --> 04:22:01.980
[Guest]: this thing has come,

04:22:01.980 --> 04:22:03.180
[Guest]: you have written about it.

04:22:03.180 --> 04:22:04.060
[Guest]: Can you please help me

04:22:04.060 --> 04:22:05.660
[Guest]: understand what has changed?

04:22:05.660 --> 04:22:06.620
[Guest]: I called three people,

04:22:06.620 --> 04:22:07.180
[Guest]: a lawyer,

04:22:07.180 --> 04:22:08.460
[Guest]: someone at a law firm,

04:22:08.460 --> 04:22:09.820
[Guest]: someone at a think tank.

04:22:09.820 --> 04:22:10.940
[Guest]: That was a unanimous answer.

04:22:11.740 --> 04:22:12.240
[Guest]: So I,

04:22:12.860 --> 04:22:13.500
[Guest]: and then, you know,

04:22:14.140 --> 04:22:14.700
[Guest]: a colleague of mine

04:22:14.700 --> 04:22:15.900
[Guest]: who had connections in the MHA,

04:22:15.900 --> 04:22:17.340
[Guest]: he got like an inside person.

04:22:17.340 --> 04:22:18.220
[Guest]: And I think that is the way

04:22:18.220 --> 04:22:19.180
[Guest]: to do a story.

04:22:19.180 --> 04:22:20.620
[Guest]: You cover all aspects.

04:22:21.260 --> 04:22:22.700
[Guest]: So I went and

04:22:23.420 --> 04:22:24.140
[Guest]: explained,

04:22:24.140 --> 04:22:24.700
[Guest]: ki boss,

04:22:25.580 --> 04:22:26.220
[Guest]: there is no,

04:22:27.020 --> 04:22:28.140
[Guest]: like, there's nothing here,

04:22:28.140 --> 04:22:29.020
[Guest]: like there's no story.

04:22:30.460 --> 04:22:31.580
[Guest]: The story is that it's just,

04:22:32.700 --> 04:22:33.740
[Guest]: so this event

04:22:33.740 --> 04:22:35.820
[Guest]: was the point of coverage,

04:22:35.820 --> 04:22:36.860
[Guest]: but in the larger level,

04:22:36.860 --> 04:22:37.580
[Guest]: nothing had changed.

04:22:37.580 --> 04:22:38.540
[Guest]: So what,

04:22:38.540 --> 04:22:39.500
[Guest]: and I'll tell you

04:22:39.500 --> 04:22:40.860
[Guest]: how it connects to processes.

04:22:40.860 --> 04:22:41.820
[Guest]: In the press,

04:22:41.820 --> 04:22:43.340
[Guest]: this issue was reported as

04:22:43.340 --> 04:22:44.460
[Guest]: Congress versus BJP.

04:22:45.660 --> 04:22:46.160
[Guest]: Okay.

04:22:46.540 --> 04:22:48.300
[Guest]: That opposition is saying

04:22:48.300 --> 04:22:49.020
[Guest]: how bad

04:22:50.300 --> 04:22:51.500
[Guest]: BJP is doing this.

04:22:52.140 --> 04:22:53.340
[Guest]: Then you get some context.

04:22:53.980 --> 04:22:55.340
[Guest]: When 2008 or 9,

04:22:55.340 --> 04:22:56.700
[Guest]: when the IT Act was passed,

04:22:56.700 --> 04:22:57.260
[Guest]: okay,

04:22:57.260 --> 04:22:58.140
[Guest]: Congress was in power,

04:22:59.180 --> 04:22:59.500
[Guest]: right?

04:22:59.500 --> 04:23:00.220
[Guest]: And they passed

04:23:00.940 --> 04:23:01.980
[Guest]: what people were,

04:23:01.980 --> 04:23:02.620
[Guest]: you know,

04:23:02.620 --> 04:23:03.740
[Guest]: gali galoching on the internet.

04:23:04.380 --> 04:23:05.020
[Unknown]: And this law,

04:23:05.020 --> 04:23:05.980
[Guest]: I think IT Act passed

04:23:05.980 --> 04:23:07.660
[Guest]: in 10 minutes in the parliament.

04:23:07.660 --> 04:23:08.700
[Guest]: Kuch debate bhi nahi hua.

04:23:08.700 --> 04:23:09.500
[Guest]: Because you know what?

04:23:10.300 --> 04:23:11.980
[Guest]: Surveillance is about power.

04:23:11.980 --> 04:23:13.340
[Guest]: It is not about

04:23:13.340 --> 04:23:14.700
[Guest]: party A versus party B.

04:23:14.700 --> 04:23:15.500
[Guest]: Everyone in power

04:23:16.300 --> 04:23:16.940
[Guest]: wants to,

04:23:17.980 --> 04:23:19.500
[Guest]: does not want your life to be private.

04:23:20.060 --> 04:23:21.580
[Guest]: That's how this power works.

04:23:22.300 --> 04:23:22.940
[Guest]: Now,

04:23:22.940 --> 04:23:23.420
[Guest]: Congress,

04:23:23.420 --> 04:23:24.540
[Guest]: who was in power at that time,

04:23:24.540 --> 04:23:26.380
[Guest]: is now taking the moral authority,

04:23:26.380 --> 04:23:27.100
[Guest]: ki yeh galat kar rahe hain,

04:23:27.100 --> 04:23:28.300
[Guest]: jab ki kuch change hi nahi hua hai.

04:23:29.180 --> 04:23:30.540
[Unknown]: Juki yeh Congress hi nahi kiya hai.

04:23:30.540 --> 04:23:31.260
[Unknown]: Congress nahi kiya hai,

04:23:31.260 --> 04:23:31.500
[Unknown]: right?

04:23:31.500 --> 04:23:32.460
[Unknown]: And the others were,

04:23:32.460 --> 04:23:33.340
[Guest]: ki everyone wants this,

04:23:33.340 --> 04:23:34.540
[Guest]: because everyone benefits,

04:23:34.540 --> 04:23:35.020
[Guest]: in a way.

04:23:35.020 --> 04:23:35.580
[Guest]: But,

04:23:35.580 --> 04:23:36.860
[Guest]: you look at the news coverage,

04:23:37.500 --> 04:23:38.780
[Guest]: that was the story.

04:23:38.780 --> 04:23:39.900
[Guest]: Congress said this,

04:23:39.900 --> 04:23:40.860
[Guest]: BJP said this.

04:23:40.860 --> 04:23:42.060
[Guest]: This is what I am describing.

04:23:42.060 --> 04:23:42.700
[Guest]: And you know,

04:23:42.700 --> 04:23:43.500
[Guest]: I was so sad,

04:23:43.500 --> 04:23:44.860
[Guest]: because my story,

04:23:44.860 --> 04:23:46.060
[Guest]: andar page pe tha.

04:23:46.060 --> 04:23:46.860
[Guest]: Yeh nothing has changed.

04:23:46.860 --> 04:23:47.900
[Guest]: Front page pe story tha,

04:23:47.900 --> 04:23:48.620
[Guest]: Congress says this,

04:23:48.620 --> 04:23:49.340
[Guest]: BJP says this.

04:23:49.340 --> 04:23:49.820
[Guest]: So,

04:23:49.820 --> 04:23:51.180
[Guest]: that day I could not understand,

04:23:51.180 --> 04:23:51.660
[Guest]: when,

04:23:51.660 --> 04:23:53.100
[Guest]: how can my paper,

04:23:53.100 --> 04:23:54.140
[Guest]: publish a story saying,

04:23:54.140 --> 04:23:54.780
[Guest]: andar,

04:23:54.780 --> 04:23:55.900
[Guest]: yeh nothing has changed.

04:23:55.900 --> 04:23:56.860
[Guest]: Or front page pe,

04:23:56.860 --> 04:23:57.900
[Guest]: you are amplifying,

04:23:57.900 --> 04:23:58.940
[Guest]: Congress, BJP.

04:23:58.940 --> 04:23:59.900
[Guest]: So, this is the problem

04:23:59.900 --> 04:24:01.420
[Guest]: with event-based reporting.

04:24:01.980 --> 04:24:03.180
[Guest]: Where you don't know,

04:24:03.180 --> 04:24:04.380
[Guest]: at a system level,

04:24:04.380 --> 04:24:05.260
[Guest]: you know what is happening.

