[Guest]: the deeper reasons,

04:25:06.300 --> 04:25:07.580
[Guest]: why we went there.

04:25:07.580 --> 04:25:09.340
[Guest]: And to get to this whole process,

04:25:09.340 --> 04:25:10.460
[Guest]: you can use,

04:25:10.460 --> 04:25:12.060
[Guest]: systems thinking approach,

