[Guest]: to say,

04:25:53.260 --> 04:25:53.500
[Guest]: you know,

04:25:53.500 --> 04:25:54.380
[Guest]: you are a good reporter.

04:25:54.380 --> 04:25:54.860
[Guest]: You know,

04:25:54.860 --> 04:25:55.180
[Guest]: you,

04:25:55.180 --> 04:25:55.820
[Guest]: all of those things,

04:25:55.820 --> 04:25:55.980
[Guest]: right?

04:25:55.980 --> 04:25:56.300
[Guest]: I'm saying,

04:25:57.020 --> 04:25:58.300
[Guest]: in every action,

04:25:58.300 --> 04:25:59.020
[Guest]: there is no,

04:25:59.020 --> 04:26:02.700
[Guest]: there is no, that this is one piece of the system that is broken.

04:26:02.700 --> 04:26:04.380
[Guest]: Once you look at the big picture,

04:26:04.380 --> 04:26:07.100
[Guest]: and instead of looking at incidents in isolation,

04:26:07.100 --> 04:26:07.420
[Guest]: you say,

04:26:07.420 --> 04:26:07.980
[Guest]: okay,

04:26:07.980 --> 04:26:09.900
[Guest]: how is the system interacting with each other?

04:26:10.540 --> 04:26:10.780
[Guest]: Right?

04:26:11.740 --> 04:26:12.220
[Guest]: And how,

04:26:12.940 --> 04:26:13.740
[Guest]: a small change,

