04:26:18.540 --> 04:26:21.340
[Guest]: Then you see the complexity of the system and you realize that,

04:26:21.340 --> 04:26:23.180
[Guest]: the problem is much more complicated.

04:26:23.180 --> 04:26:24.300
[Guest]: You can't just,

04:26:24.300 --> 04:26:25.100
[Guest]: fix one part,

04:26:25.740 --> 04:26:26.860
[Guest]: and think that,

04:26:26.860 --> 04:26:29.020
[Guest]: fix it 10 times in isolation,

04:26:29.020 --> 04:26:29.980
[Guest]: the system will,

04:26:29.980 --> 04:26:31.180
