[Guest]: In a way that,

04:26:32.060 --> 04:26:33.580
[Guest]: about the process that,

04:26:33.580 --> 04:26:35.340
[Guest]: it's not just one event.

04:26:35.340 --> 04:26:36.860
[Guest]: Because if you just look at event,

04:26:36.860 --> 04:26:37.580
[Guest]: in that whole system,

04:26:37.580 --> 04:26:38.380
[Guest]: you're looking at X.

04:26:39.100 --> 04:26:39.980
[Guest]: You've forgotten,

04:26:39.980 --> 04:26:41.420
[Guest]: how we got to X.

04:26:41.420 --> 04:26:42.380
[Guest]: And that is the story,

04:26:42.380 --> 04:26:43.340
[Guest]: not X.

04:26:43.340 --> 04:26:45.980
