[Guest]: combining with

05:09:51.300 --> 05:09:52.100
[Guest]: knowing about your body

05:09:52.100 --> 05:09:53.060
[Guest]: and data in that way.

05:09:53.060 --> 05:09:54.420
[Amit Varma]: Yeah, like I'm not asking you

05:09:54.420 --> 05:09:55.540
[Amit Varma]: for prescriptive advice.

05:09:56.580 --> 05:09:57.300
[Amit Varma]: But just yeah,

05:09:57.300 --> 05:09:58.420
[Amit Varma]: what was your journey like?

05:09:58.420 --> 05:09:59.220
[Amit Varma]: What was your thinking?

05:09:59.220 --> 05:10:00.180
[Amit Varma]: What did you discover?

05:10:00.980 --> 05:10:01.700
[Unknown]: And you know,

05:10:01.700 --> 05:10:03.140
[Amit Varma]: how did you build the habits

05:10:03.140 --> 05:10:04.980
[Amit Varma]: that you built around fitness?

05:10:04.980 --> 05:10:05.700
[Guest]: All of that.

